title: (Weds Early Bird) The Most Trouble We Got In School + Why Lunchbox Went Through Airbnb’s Belongings + Dumb Debate of the Day: Nachos with a Fork??
itunes:title: (Weds Early Bird) The Most Trouble We Got In School + Why Lunchbox Went Through Airbnb’s Belongings + Dumb Debate of the Day: Nachos with a Fork??
description:
We reveal the most trouble we ever got in during school. Lunchbox just discovered Airbnb and decided to go through the owner’s possessions to learn things about him. He reports back on his findings and why he thinks Airbnb is life changing. Amy brings us the Dumb Debate of the Day after her friend thought it may be a red flag that her date at his nachos with a fork.
